---
title: Mediterranean Beef Rissoles & Cheesy Wedges with Cucumber Salad & Herby Mayo
description: Beef mince can raise rissoles to number one in our dinner time charts. They are the fan-fav’ when you can dip them in a herby mayo. The secret to fame for this dish is melting Parmesan cheese over golden wedges.
